Figshare,allows,researchers,to,publish,all,of,their,research,online,in,an,easily,citable,sharable,and,discoverable,manner,All,file,formats,can,be,published,including,videos,and,datasets,Creative,commons,licensing,permits,research,to,be,easily,shared,while,still,allowing,researchers,to,maintain,ownership,of,their,findings,Figshare,gives,users,unlimited,public,space,and,GB,of,private,storage,space,for,free,The,figshare,API,enables,other,programs,to,make,use,of,figshare,s,functionality,and,content,This,API,employs,REST,calls,and,can,be,accessed,and,used,by,anyone